   |------------------+-----------------------------------------------------|
   | move             | De toets Move.                                      |
   |------------------+-----------------------------------------------------|
   | next             | De toets Next.                                      |
   |------------------+-----------------------------------------------------|
   | open             | De toets Open.                                      |
